&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The human brain is the most complex object in the universe, yet society had accepted one-size-fits all approaches to cognition. The “solutions” (think coffee, energy drinks, and even a friend’s rx) were mediocre at best and frankly, made no sense to us. So, we created Thesis, the world’s first customized nootropics company. If you’ve never heard that word before, it’s just a fancy way of saying brain supplements. In five years, most will be taking nootropics on the daily and chances are, they’ll be ours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With an exceptional efficacy rate, the world has taken notice — we’ve raised over $14M in venture capital, garnered interest from leading neuroscientists and athletes, and established ourselves as the industry’s leading brand. Now, we’re looking for incredible people to help us share the gift of enhanced cognitive function with the world. If you’re looking to be a part of a movement — one that involves both immense self-growth and an ambitious mission to pioneer an industry — we’d love to have you on the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Head of Performance Creative to own our paid creative strategy end to end: ideation, briefing, production, testing, and iteration. You will build the system that turns consumer insight into winning ads — and keep that system getting faster and smarter over time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You grew up in paid media. You know what makes someone stop scrolling, read the next line, and buy. You have studied thousands of ads — what worked, what flopped, and why — and you have developed real conviction about the craft.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You also understand that creative is the most underleveraged variable in paid performance. Not the audience. Not the bid. The creative.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Creative Strategy&lt;/strong&gt; Own the creative strategy across all paid channels — Meta, TikTok, YouTube, programmatic, and wherever the next high-ROI channel emerges. You know how to structure a test, read the signal, and scale what is working. You do not wait for data to tell you what to test next. You already have a hypothesis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brief Writing &amp;amp; Insight Mining&lt;/strong&gt; You write briefs that give editors and creators a clear target. You mine insight from reviews, support tickets, social comments, competitor ads, and anywhere real people talk about real problems. You know how to turn a one-star review into a winning hook.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Creative Testing &amp;amp; Iteration&lt;/strong&gt; Build and run a structured testing framework across hooks, formats, offers, and angles. Own the loop between performance data and creative output. Know when to kill something and when to double down. Keep the machine learning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Video-First Production&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee the creative studio for performance content including: VSLs, short-form social ads, UGC-style content, testimonials, and hybrid formats. Know how to direct a shoot and how to direct an edit. Understand the difference between a video that looks good and a video that converts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Landing Page &amp;amp; Funnel Creative&lt;/strong&gt; Own the creative expression from ad to landing page. Write copy, design concepts, and test messaging across the full funnel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team &amp;amp; Freelancer Management&lt;/strong&gt; Build and manage a team of editors, writers, and creators. Develop strong freelancer and UGC creator relationships. Set a high bar. Give clear direction. Get great work out of people without slowing everything down.&lt;/p&gt;
