&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring an AI-first Retention Product Manager to own the customer&#39;s post-purchase product experience and the operating systems behind our retention programs. This includes app and portal onboarding, subscription management, post-purchase education, loyalty and referral programs, and the AI-enabled production and QA workflows that power our lifecycle marketing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hybrid role for someone with strong lifecycle fundamentals who has grown into product thinking: defining requirements, shipping improvements with engineering, instrumenting outcomes, and treating AI as a core capability rather than a tool they occasionally use. You can build a Klaviyo flow yourself — but you&#39;d rather build the system that produces a hundred of them reliably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You’ll Make an Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own retention-impacting product surfaces: app and portal onboarding, subscription management, account experience, and post-purchase education.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and operate AI-enabled production systems for retention — briefing, email/flow build, QA, research, and reporting workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate retention strategy into product requirements and ship improvements in partnership with product, engineering, and design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run experiments that span product and lifecycle touchpoints: in-app prompts paired with email/SMS journeys, cancellation-save experiences, education sequences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and operate loyalty, referral, VIP, and advocacy programs — platform selection, integration, and lifecycle activation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute hands-on in Klaviyo when needed: flows, segmentation, QA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Instrument retention product work so impact is measurable: event tracking, dashboards, experiment readouts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document systems and processes so workflows scale beyond you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
