&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience spanning lifecycle marketing and product management — you&#39;ve owned a product surface or shipped product work, not just campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A demonstrated AI-native working style: you build with AI tools daily, design workflows around them, and know where they fail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical fluency: APIs, webhooks, integrations, automation platforms, and basic data work. You don&#39;t need engineering for everything.&lt;/li&gt;
